folder: Springfield Boulevard & Murdock Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Springfield Boulevard, west side, at Murdock Avenue, showing one of the Hendrickson houses. In 1891 it was owned by Ino. C. Hendrickson and in 1918 by C. Tracy. This was also known as the Werner farmhouse. See other views on Springfield Road for other Hendrickson homes.

1922
